                            <title xml:lang="en" type="desc">Hurufi Chronicle</title>
                            <note>Dated the beginning of Dhu'l-Qa'da, 1191/Dec. 22, 1776. Browne
                                notes two other copies of this work, E. 4 and E. 13, and a further
                                copy in the British Museum (Or. 5961).</note>
                            <incipit/>
